#~ "See /usr/share/doc/samba-doc/htmldocs/Samba3-Developers-Guide/pwencrypt."
#~ "html from the samba-doc package for more details."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Meer informatie vindt u in /usr/share/doc/samba-doc/htmldocs/Samba3-"
